snippet.title: AVGN Game Over World 1- 8 Playthough
snippet.description:
This game is pretty old so expect some glitches here and there.
Not sure that developer will upload a fix. If I'm not mistaken, this was made on an old engine and he would have to remake the game from the ground up.
